{"tid":1505370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"之後塞鐵又好 塞機場又好 最重要係一樣嘢","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:30:46.000Z","uid":72301,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1d566744d6962b4331eb67c2f3396caf0a5e7f","tid":1505370,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"係禮貌啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不合作運動唔同平時對警犬講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你對政府嘅不合作運動始終會影響好多市民<br />\n我地始終係騎劫緊佢地用公共設施嘅自由<br />\n即使我地幾有道理都好<br />\n都要記住be humble！<br />\n無啦啦比人阻到仲要比我地鬧 係人都有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以希望手足忍讓多啲 <br />\n唔好隨便爆粗圍人 多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e9718bbb8470a1213fb7b60be21c27e0ef533a60","tid":1505370,"uid":72301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"我知罵不還口係好難<br />\n但如果我地能夠忍辱負重<br />\n先顯出我地嘅質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70116bdb002ec8afcfdc4e0b5c289c5788ffc94d","tid":1505370,"uid":63482,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:55:41.000Z","msg":"共產黨起家都係咁，對國民黨趕盡殺絕，對平民就秋毫不犯。<br />\n<br />\n禮多人不怪，多個支持者好過多個敵人。"},{"pid":"e2afad3fb233e79c7f1c5cc60cdef7ad85a7d646","tid":1505370,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,待定, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機9月6(五)搞埋</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n國泰城改左828 (三)，被炒機師空姐需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7808312be847a6ece1f95fa90223dd64984c51c","tid":1505370,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196811725f36c441ac664a27235a9599a27c67a6","tid":1505370,"uid":72301,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:02:45.000Z","msg":"仲有之前都有巴打講過<br />\n點塞都要比返個希望人地<br />\n<br />\n我地可以拖慢佢嘅效率 但唔好完全令佢停擺<br />\n機場10條check in隊我地可以霸9條<br />\n但點都應該網開一面 比到佢地有排隊嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n塞鐵同樣道理 塞幾架之後要放生一班人<br />\n之後先再塞<br />\n咁樣先易減少衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fe6fbb9db6c2bd268aae4bd3557ac2f2af1f9d","tid":1505370,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"推啊！"},{"pid":"b965e8d3b778d3f39f3a3fc6393682bbfd05277a","tid":1505370,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"各有各做！"},{"pid":"132ed5950a516589f5a934bf9cc23f9b49aa3542","tid":1505370,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22f47466398f14f361b09d93093d9a1f09738a28","tid":1505370,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,